{"article_id":"GNMkI2KvjjhM7aPk","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Donald Trump ' s bloodthirsty threat","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"to have protesters in Minneapolis shot by the military ,","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"issued in a tweet early Friday morning ,","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"prompted Twitter to restrict access to the president ' s message ,","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"ruling","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"that it violated the social network ' s policy against \" glorifying violence. \"","depth":4},{"id":6,"text":"In the tweet ,","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"posted just before 1 a.m. Eastern Time ,","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"Trump first wrote","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"that","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"\" THUGS are dishonoring the memory of George Floyd , \" the black man","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"whose killing on Monday by a Minneapolis police officer","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"who knelt on his throat","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"as he gasped for air","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"has prompted protests and rage .","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"The president then threatened to have soldiers open fire","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"unless local authorities in Minneapolis regain control ,","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"adding ,","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"\" when the looting starts ,","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"the shooting starts. \"","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"The tweet was soon covered by an initial warning message ,","depth":5},{"id":21,"text":"which said","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"the president ' s comments violated the platform ' s rules ,","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"but had not been removed","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"because \" it may be in the public ' s interest \" to be able to read them .","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"Readers","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"who clicked past that screen","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"were able to read the inflammatory tweet , but with the warning message above it .","depth":5},{"id":28,"text":"Mayor Frey responds to the President ' s tweets :","depth":4},{"id":29,"text":"Weakness is refusing to take responsibility for your own actions .","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"Weakness is pointing your finger at somebody else during a time of crisis .","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"Donald Trump knows nothing about the strength of Minneapolis .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"We are strong as hell ..","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"pic.twitter.com/BtMyjrA6on - Acyn Torabi","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"( @ Acyn )","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"May 29 , 2020","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"\" Well , let me say this , \"","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"Frey responded .","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"\" Weakness is refusing to take responsibility for your own actions .","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"Weakness is pointing your finger at somebody else during a time of crisis .","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"Donald Trump knows nothing about the strength of Minneapolis .","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"We are strong as hell .","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"Is this a difficult time period ?","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"Yes .","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"But you better be damn sure","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"that we ' re going to get through this. \"","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"Later on Friday ,","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"after the police officer","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"seen on video","depth":13},{"id":49,"text":"killing Floyd ,","depth":13},{"id":50,"text":"Derek Chauvin ,","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"was arrested","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"and charged with third-degree murder and manslaughter ,","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"the mayor described that \" as an essential first step \" in a tweet of his own .","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"The man","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"who killed George Floyd","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"has been charged with murder .","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"This an essential first step on a much longer road toward justice","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"and healing our city .","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"- Mayor Jacob Frey","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"( @ MayorFrey )","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"May 29 , 2020","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"Trump ,","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"who had been expected to address the killing of Floyd , and his own provocative taunt , at a White House news conference ,","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"instead confined his remarks to inflaming tensions with China ,","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"by changing the terms of the U.S. relationship to Hong Kong","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"and declaring a full withdrawal from the World Health Organization ,","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"before departing","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"without taking a single question .","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"The President escapes his own press conference","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"to evade questions on Minneapolis","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"pic.twitter.com/e7jKzlvlTL","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"- Acyn Torabi","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"( @ Acyn )","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"May 29 , 2020","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"His administration did , however , devote some time to trying to dodge the Twitter restriction ,","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"by using the White House Twitter feed","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"to quote the president ' s inflammatory rhetoric .","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"That White House tweet was soon restricted too , with the same warning label .","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"Anger over Trump ' s rhetoric spread widely on Friday .","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"Chicago ' s Mayor Lori Lightfoot called Trump ' s comment \" profoundly dangerous . \"","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"Lori Lightfoot not holding back on Trump !","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"pic.twitter.com/rNOVT8D42N - ? ? arcusD ? ?","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"( @ _MarcusD3_ )","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"May 29 , 2020","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"\" His goal is to polarize ,","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"to destabilize local government","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"and inflame racist urges , \"","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"she added .","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"\" And we can not , absolutely not , let him prevail .","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"And I will code what I really want to say to Donald Trump .","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"It ' s two words ,","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"it begins with ' F '","depth":13},{"id":93,"text":"and it ends with ' you.","depth":13},{"id":94,"text":"' I will not remain silent","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"while this man cynically tries to turn this incredibly painful moment into one for his own political gain. \"","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"Twitter ' s decision","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"to draw a line for Trump","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"came just hours after he issued an executive order","depth":7},{"id":99,"text":"threatening to make it easier for users to file lawsuits against the company for perceived political bias .","depth":7},{"id":100,"text":"The order was a transparent act of retaliation against the company","depth":6},{"id":101,"text":"for having appended a fact-checking note to a tweet","depth":7},{"id":102,"text":"in which Trump made a range of false claims about plans for California","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"to make it easier for registered voters to vote by mail during the ongoing pandemic .","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"Jameel Jaffer , the executive director of the Knight First Amendment Institute at Columbia University , told Adweek","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"that the executive order itself violated the First Amendment","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"because it was an act of government retaliation .","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"\" The order was born unconstitutional","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"because it was issued in retaliation for Twitter ' s fact-checking of President Trump ' s tweets , \"","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"Jaffer said .","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"\" The First Amendment protects Twitter ' s right","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"to respond to the president ' s speech ,","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"including by attaching warnings to tweets","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"that glorify violence , \"","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"Jaffer said in a statement","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"sent to .","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"\" Fundamentally this dispute is about whether Twitter has the right","depth":8},{"id":117,"text":"to disagree with , criticize , and respond to the president .","depth":8},{"id":118,"text":"Obviously , it does .","depth":8},{"id":119,"text":"It is remarkable and truly chilling that the president and his advisers seem to believe otherwise. \"","depth":8},{"id":120,"text":"Jaffer ' s colleague Katie Fallow , a senior attorney at the First Amendment Institute , noted","depth":6},{"id":121,"text":"that unusual language","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"that appeared to have been added to the order","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"without much review ,","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"\" make the retaliatory motive even clearer . \"","depth":7},{"id":125,"text":"Exhibit one million in 1st Amendment claim of government retaliation .","depth":5},{"id":126,"text":"https : //t.co/tYq8cfFhXS","depth":5},{"id":127,"text":"- Katie Fallow","depth":6},{"id":128,"text":"( @ KatieFallow )","depth":6},{"id":129,"text":"May 28 , 2020","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":259,"left":157,"right":258,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":157,"left":135,"right":156,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":135,"left":133,"right":134,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":133,"left":132,"right":3,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":132,"left":131,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":131,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":134,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":156,"left":148,"right":155,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":148,"left":143,"right":147,"relatio